{
  "text": "Under (Lorentz) global conformal transformation, the L.H.S of (3.4) transforms as, It is well known that Cachazo-Strominger subleading soft graviton theorem [CITATION_1] is equivalent to the (superrotation) conformal Ward identity [CITATION_2] ,",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "115294846",
